</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>4. MUSEUMS</strong></h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>4.1.  </strong><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/A22fc73V9oyK5Bjy8" class="ek-link"><strong>Ja</strong></a><strong><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/A22fc73V9oyK5Bjy8" class="ek-link">ntar Mantar O</a><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/A22fc73V9oyK5Bjy8" target="_blank" aria-label="bservatory (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">bservatory</a></strong></h3>



