<p class="has-text-align-justify">This is my very first trip to <strong>Jaipur City, the capital of Rajasthan States</strong> of India. Always heard that it is a good destination for the traveller in India (foreigners as well). Over the years seeing a lot of travel stories regarding this also, so I always wanted to explore. Finally, it’s happening for <strong><a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://blog.sukantapal.com/microsoft-techvista-2014-at-jaipur-india/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">Microsoft Research Events</a></strong> in India Called <strong>Microsoft Tech Vista 2014</strong> at Deep Smriti Auditorium, Tagore International School in Jaipur, Rajasthan.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1592" height="1200" src="https://blog.sukantapal.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sukanta33115_Sukanta-Pal_LR.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-450"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Sukanta Pal inside of Hawa Mahal Castle.</figcaption></figure>



<p class="has-text-align-justify">Those days buying tickets is a hassle, for that you need to go nearest train station or travel agents for tickets and also print with higher price. When ticket booking done and taking print out also, it’s time to count days with excitement for travel. </p>



