<p class="has-text-align-justify">Train Number <strong>12987 &#8211; AJMR Express </strong>was on 21st Juanray 2014, when reached Sealdah Railway Station know that train resecheduled on 22nd Juanray 2014 depart at 4:00 am from Platfrom 9A/9B. No Interent facality on Phone, that’s why didn’t know eariler, waited at Railway Station and spent midnight awake with over cup of coffees.</p>



